HEADWORD: Agedness
<hw>A"ged*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being aged;
oldness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Custom without truth is but <qex>agedness</qex> of error.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

